---|------|\n| Host / Session / 工作区 / 错误码 | `技术设计文档/19` + `需求/00` / `06` |\n| 存取 Port / IO 落点 / validate 读盘解耦 | `技术设计文档/23`；回写 `18` / `19` / `20` / 引擎 README |\n| 选型 / 拓扑 | `技术设计文档/05`、`18` |\n| 导出 / 版本拒载 | `技术设计文档/07`、`17` |\n| 产品行为 / UX / 验收 | `需求/` 对应编号 |\n| 代码落地模块地图 | 用户明示后写 `docs/AI/` |\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":42,"fileSize":3108,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.cursor/rules/docs-execution.mdc","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":42},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-96d3dfb4-6d47-457e-be71-5397f5f70fa5-4\nfc_d956bc5d-42ff-95ff-bcc6-ae5b2f48f033_3","startedAtMs":"1784787092677","completedAtMs":"1784787093075"},"model_call_id":"f7d5a74b-9eeb-4270-bc9b-336a0481ff48-1-anyl","session_id":"5dd45cc9-1e8c-4bbc-b17e-4454504d0abe","timestamp_ms":1784787093051}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-96d3dfb4-6d47-457e-be71-5397f5f70fa5-5\nfc_d956bc5d-42ff-95ff-bcc6-ae5b2f48f033_4","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.cursor/rules/engine-boundaries.mdc"},"result":{"success":{"content":"---\ndescription: packages/rpg-engine 纯引擎边界\nglobs: packages/rpg-engine/**\nalwaysApply: false\n---\n\n# 引擎包边界（rpg-engine）\n\n详情：[05](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/05-技术选型与工程边界.md)、[19](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)、[**23**](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)、[02](../../docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md)。\n\n## 必须执行\n\n- **禁止** import：`react`、`react-dom`、`next`、`@xyflow/*`。\n- **禁止** `window` / `document` / `localStorage`（测试可注入）。\n- **EngineHost 单例**由 server/壳持有；本包提供 create/host API。\n- **CallSession** 在 Host 内存；`frozenCard`；同 user 通话互斥。\n- Composer 只读；EffectExecutor 仅出口/Free 管线；工具只登记 candidate。\n- **FreeCallPostPipeline** 为 Free 挂机唯一总入口（可注入）；v1 = 有效门闩 + MemoryCommit +（有 candidate 则 ExitSelector）；禁 transcript 隐式扫描。\n- Free Session.`packageId === \"__free__\"`；禁止 load 该哨兵为故事目录。\n- 媒介经 **EffectSink**；逻辑写 Profile 在 Executor。\n- **存取：** 经 Port 注入（Content / Profile / Memory / EngineLog，见技术设计 [23](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)）；**禁止**本包内长期保留 `node:fs` / `better-sqlite3` 实现。本机实现落在 `apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/`。磁盘布局约定见 [19](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)，由 IO 模块解释路径。\n- 本包只被 Next **server**（`app/api` / `*.server.ts` / `utils/server`）/ 壳 / Vitest 引用；**禁止** Studio V2 Client（含 `bis` / `pageComponents` / `typeFiles` / `ajaxProxy`）任何 import（含 type）。\n- 条件求值结构化谓词；禁 `eval`。\n- **对外门面：** `src/index.ts` **允许且鼓励**聚合导出；**合法调用方**只 `import from \"@airpc/rpg-engine\"`，禁依赖方深挖内部模块。\n- **测试**放 `packages/rpg-engine/tests/`，禁止与 `src/` 平放 `*.test.ts`。\n- **目录职责聚类：** 内部域文件增多时按异责 ≥4 分子目录（host/session/memory…）；不为空壳先建单文件空目录。\n\n## 默认执行\n\n- 公共导出收敛于包入口；Port 接口在本包；LLM/Realtime 实现不进本包。\n- Effect plan / ledger / 锁决策表遵循需求 16、19。\n- Vitest 覆盖 Resolver、Exit、Free pipeline、Profile 隔离、幂等；IO 测用假 Port 或注入。\n\n## 禁止事项\n\n- GPIO / ALSA / 旧 relay / expertReferral 上帝模块。\n- 把 React Flow layout 当运行真源。\n- 强迫 Studio 深引引擎内部路径「绕过门面」。\n- 引擎 import `apps/studioV2/engineIOModule`（或任何 Studio 路径）。","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":39,"fileSize":2843,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.cursor/rules/engine-boundaries.mdc","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":39},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-96d3dfb4-6d47-457e-be71-5397f5f70fa5-5\nfc_d956bc5d-42ff-95ff-bcc6-ae5b2f48f033_4","startedAtMs":"1784787092953","completedAtMs":"1784787093198"},"model_call_id":"f7d5a74b-9eeb-4270-bc9b-336a0481ff48-1-anyl","session_id":"5dd45cc9-1e8c-4bbc-b17e-4454504d0abe","timestamp_ms":1784787093136}
